item.description:
Use Vitest to create a few basic unit test for the algorithims in the previous lessons.
npm init -y npm i -D vitest Update the package.json with a test script.
file_type_npm package.json &#34;scripts&#34;: { &#34;test&#34;: &#34;vitest&#34; }, Vitest Basic Example import { expect, test } from &#39;vitest&#39;; import { cumSum } from &#39;./sum&#39;; test(&#39;cumulative sum of an array&#39;, () =&gt; { expect(cumSum([1, 3, 5, 7])).toBe(16); expect(cumSum([-2, -4, -8])).toBe(-14); });
